{"name":"葛城ミサト","nameCn":"葛城美里","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/04/fc/5088_crt_anidb.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>葛城美里</li><li><span>别名: </span>葛城ミサト</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>かつらぎ ミサト</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Katsuragi Misato</li><li><span>性别: </span>女</li><li><span>生日: </span>1986-12-08</li><li><span>血型: </span>A型</li><li><span>身高: </span>163cm</li><li><span>体重: </span>47kg</li><li><span>BWH: </span>B:88/W:59/H:82</li><li><span>引用来源: </span>anidb.net</li>","detail":"葛城美里（日语：葛城 ミサト、英语：Katsuragi Misato）是日本动画《新世纪福音战士》当中人物。她是NERV的指挥官，军衔最初为大尉，TV动画第12话时晋升为少佐，在新剧场版中则为中佐。她在NERV的任务包括指挥及监视EVA驾驶员、构思及发布攻击策略，与赤木律子协调EVA技术支援及测试也是她的工作，她同时也是碇真嗣与惣流·明日香·兰格雷的监护人。<br /><br />在故事一开始时，美里将真嗣带入NERV，并说服他担任初号机的驾驶员。后来她要求真嗣跟她一同生活，后来明日香也与他们居住在同一栋公寓。随着故事进行，美里从旧情人加持良治那里得知人类补完计划的面貌及埋藏在NERV深处的秘密。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/34218","name":"NEON GENESIS EVANGELION ADDITION","nameCn":"","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/db/fc/34218_jp.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/910","name":"NEON GENESIS EVANGELION 10TH ANNIVERSARY - DECADE","nameCn":"新世纪福音战士原声音乐 十周年纪念CD [DECADE]","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/e2/05/910_965v9.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":""},{"href":"/subject/265","name":"新世紀エヴァンゲリオン","nameCn":"新世纪福音战士","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/e5/69/265_Z5Uou.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"三石琴乃","castHref":"/person/3918","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/85/9b/3918_seiyu_anidb.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/3302","name":"ヱヴァンゲリヲン新劇場版:破","nameCn":"福音战士新剧场版：破","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/6f/ab/3302_rEfZV.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"三石琴乃","castHref":"/person/3918","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/85/9b/3918_seiyu_anidb.jpg"},{"href":"/subject/772","name":"ヱヴァンゲリヲン新劇場版:序","nameCn":"福音战士新剧场版：序","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/e5/7c/772_yFW6i.jpg","staff":"配角","cast":"三石琴乃","castHref":"/person/3918","castTag":"CV